\c 1
\s Kukwira kwaJesu kudenga
\p
\v 1 Rugwaro rwokutanga ndakarwuita Teofiro, nezvose Jesu zvaakatanga kuita nokudzidzisa,
\v 2 kusvikira zuva raakakwidzwa, amboraira noMweya Mutsvene vapositora vaakanga asanangura;
\v 3 vaakazviratidzavo kwavari ari mupenyu shure kokutambudzika kwake nezviratidzo zvizhinji, zvisingagoni kurambwa ari mupenyu, achivonekwa navo mazuva anamakumi mana, achitaura zvinhu zvovushe bwaMwari;
\v 4 zvino avungana navo, kuti varege kubva Jerusarema asi vagarire chivimbiso chaBaba, chamakanzwa kwandiri;
\v 5 Johwani zvirokwazvo wakabhabhatidza nemvura, asi imwi muchabhabhatidzwa noMweya Mutsvene mazuva mazhinji asati apera.
\v 6 Zvino ivo vakati vavungana, vakamubvunza vachiti: Ishe, muchadzosera vushe kunavaIsraeri nenguva ino here?
\v 7 Akati kwavari: Hazvisi zvenyu kuziva nguva kana misi yakatarwa naBaba vamene nesimba ravo;
\v 8 Asi muchapiwa simba, Mweya Mutsvene avuya pamusoro penyu; ipapo muchava zvapupu zvangu paJerusarema pamwe neJudhiya rose neSamaria, nokusvikira kumugumo wenyika.
\v 9 Zvino wakati areva izvozvi, akakwidzwa vakatarira, negore rikamubvisa pazviso zvavo.
\v 10 Zvino vachitarisisa kudenga, achikwira, zvino tarira, varume vaviri vamire navo nenguvo chena;
\v 11 ivo vakati: imwi varume veGariri, makamirireiko makatarira kudenga? iyeyu Jesu, unobviswa kwamuri, achikwidzwa kudenga, uchavuya saizvozvo sezvamamuvona achienda kudenga.
\s Vadzidzi vanogarira Mweya
\p
\v 12 Zvino vakadzokera Jerusarema, vachibva pagomo rinonzi reMiorivhi, riri pedo neJerusarema, \add nhambo\add* yerwendo rwesabata.
\v 13 Vakati vapinda, vakakwira muimba yepamusoro, apo paigara Peturo, naJohwani, naJakobho, naAndiriya, naFiripi, naTomasi, naBhatironomiyo, naMatewu, naJakobho, waAerfeo, naSimoni Zeroti, naJudhasi waJakobho.
\v 14 Ava vose vakatsungirira nomoyo mumwe pakunyengetera nokukumbira, vanavakadzi naMaria mai vaJesu, navanun'una vake.
\s Vanosanangura Matia panzvimbo yaJudhasi
\p
\v 15 Zvino namazuva iwayo Peturo wakasimuka pakati pevadzidzi, kwaiva nechaunga navanhu pamwechete vanenge zana namakumi maviri, akati:
\v 16 Varume, hama, zvakafanira kuti rugwaro rwuzadziswe, Mweya Mutsvene warwakataura nomuromo waDhavhidhi, pamusoro paJudhasi, wakanga ari mutungamiriri wavaya vakabata Jesu.
\v 17 Nokuti wakanga achiverengwa pamwe chete nesu, akapiwa mugove wake pabasa iri.
\v 18 Zvino munhu uyu wakatenga munda nomubairo wezvisakarurama, akawa nemusoro, akaparuka napakati, ura hwake hwese hwukabvajukira kunze.
\v 19 Zvikanzwika navose vaigara Jerusarema; kusvikira munda uyu uchitumidzwa norurimi rwavo \add kuti\add* Akeridhama, ndokuti: Munda weropa.
\v 20 Nokuti zvakanyorwa mubhuku yaMapisarema, \add zvichinzi\add*: Musha wake ngauitwe dongo, Kurege kuva nomunhu unogaramo; Vuye: Mumwe ngaatore vutariri bwake.
\v 21 Naizvozvo zvakafanira pavarume vaifamba nesu nguva yose, Ishe Jesu yaaipinda nokubuda pakati pedu,
\v 22 kutanga parubhabhatidzo rwaJohwani, kusvikira pazuva raakabva kwatiri, achikwidzwa, mumwe wavo unofanira kuva chapupu chokumuka kwake pamwe chete nesu.
\v 23 Zvino vakamisa vaviri, vaiti: Josefa, wainzi Bhasabha, wakatumidzwavo Jusito, naMatiasi.
\v 24 Vakanyengetera, vachiti: Imwi Ishe, munoziva moyo yavose, ratidzai kuti wamunosanangura kunaivava vaviri ndoupi
\v 25 kuti apiwe chikamu pabasa novuapositora uhwu, Judhasi hwaakatorerwa nokudarika, kuti iye aende panzvimbo yake.
\v 26 Zvino vakavapa mijenya ikabata Matia; akaverengwa pamwe chete navapositora vanegumi nomumwe.
